tarck's elegantly minimal design evoked the feeling and romance of steamship travel –albeit in a totally modern way – where a cross-section of interesting world travelers gather to depart on a journey together. Royalton is still the choice of interesting people the world over.</p>    <img src="images/spacer.gif"  alt="Royalton New York Hotel"  width="100" height="65" /><br />        <img src="images/royaltonQuote1.gif" alt="Spectacular - The New York Times" title="Spectacular - The New York Times" width="245" height="90" /><br />    <img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="10" height="80" /><br />        <ul>    <li class="address"><H3>ROYALTON MANHATTAN HOTEL</H3></li>    <li class="address"><GEO TYPE="US">44 West 44th Street New York, New York 10036</GEO></li>    <li class="address">Tel. 212 869 4400 Fax 212 869 8965</li>    <li class="address">Reservations US 800 697 1791</li>    <li class="address">Reservations International 00800 4969 1780</li></noscript><!-- Main Nav --><div id="lowerhomenav"><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="8" width="5" /><br /><div class="homenav"><span class="nav"><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com"><img src="images/MHGgray.gif" alt="Morgans Hotel Group" width="180" height="12" border="0"/></a><br /><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="3" width="5" /><br /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com" title="Morgans Hotel Group Home Page">Home</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/reserve.asp" title="Online Reservations">Reservations</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/hotels.asp" title="Hotels">Hotels</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/meetings.asp"  title="Meetings and Events Services">Meetings &amp; Events</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://ww